lish\">প্রতিযোগিতামূলক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সক্ষমতা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বৃদ্ধি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অত্যন্ত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জরুরি।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নতুন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বাণিজ্য</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রতিবন্ধকতা</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">যেমন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মার্কিন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শুল্ক</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">এই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অবস্থাকে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আরও</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জটিল</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তুলেছে।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">টিকে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">থাকতে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হলে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বাংলাদেশকে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">একদিকে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যেমন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কূটনৈতিক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আলোচনা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জোরদার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করতে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হবে</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">তেমনি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অভ্যন্তরীণ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কাঠামোগত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দুর্বলতাও</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দূর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করতে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হবে।</span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">নম্বর বণ্টন:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">যথাযথভাবে অনুবাদ করার জন্য ০৫ নম্বর। কোনো লাইন মিস করলে ০১ নম্বর কর্তন </span><span class=\"english\">করা </span><span class=\"english\">হবে।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">বিশেষ দ্রষ্টব্য</span><span class=\"english\">: </span><span class=\"english\">লাইনগুলোর</span><span class=\"english\"> সঠিক</span><span class=\"english\"> ভাবানুবাদ লিখতে পারলে পূর্ণ নম্বর পাবে। আক্ষরিক অনুবাদ লেখার প্রয়োজন নেই</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\"> [</span><span class=\"english\">প্রতি ২টি বানান ভুলের জন্য ০১ নম্বর করে কর্তন করা হবে।</span><span class=\"english\">]</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">পরীক্ষক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভুলগুলো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আন্ডারলাইন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অবশ্যই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ঠিক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দিবেন</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p>"
